# Code of Conduct

## Our Pledge
We pledge to foster an open, inclusive, and harassment-free environment.  
**M-Pesa serves 61M+ daily users**—let’s mirror that inclusivity here.

## Standards
- Use welcoming language.
- Respect differing viewpoints.
- Gracefully accept constructive criticism.

## Enforcement
Violations may result in temporary/permanent bans.  
Full text: [Contributor Covenant 2.1](https://www.contributor-covenant.org/version/2/1/code_of_conduct/)